, "68eeec50-5b6d-c500-e400-cb644e4f3eff"], "h6fd4ad04gf216g4079gb810gcce55c1d9ec1": ["Illy so busy. Only cares about the book. Book this. Book that. <i>Urgh.</i>", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "97bf8f95-cc81-d680-c471-0da12aed65fc"], "h3be6b942gd8f0g45degb42egbd1a96d4e55f": ["Your name is 'Fork'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "fa81a3d3-d76d-3a5a-e724-9d8931a72b0e"], "h125081a3g4fdfg4ce6gb8d4g8bf8115a1bd0": ["Your name is 'Shovel'?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "512fef4e-65dc-9595-48a3-8405db61688c"], "h62139a4dgb458g4615g9f49g0b226c2dcebc": ["Master Illy calls me Shovel. Don't like it? Change it. ", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "ba7d27cc-4eea-5b7a-0c6d-2b455115f282"], "he0086357g9b1bg4ed0g8d25g74d5dfc9cc0d": ["What would you like to be called? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "447b14cd-cdfa-ec71-f9b5-bf745368aa8d"], "h9011824eg1897g400eg93adg43a5cd97543a": ["Don't care. ", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "e61bd36b-253c-f446-ffb6-db77b205b709"], "h7e7a6125gfc7fg4327g938bg97c88a6db2c9": ["Shovel is fine.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "fcc8ef3c-b2af-9d07-af41-7dbf8c1292a6"], "hd7eae515gd275g4ab0gad1fg77625ad237a0": ["So. What first, master? Gutting locals? Raising the dead? Making them walk? Making them scream?", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "5a5a8a7e-14f3-8d1d-d55b-f2f2844a9faf"], "hac21db3egd0abg4fb6ga757g891be25486f7": ["No. And you'll not commit such deeds in my name either.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "d0917de5-327e-b7f3-fa3a-49196a3c164b"], "ha4956289g8f29g4fd3g86e1g889747343d27": ["Is that what you and your old master did here? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "117cbb51-e439-c7d2-a117-6475cb1aec7d"], "h00fc0269g161cg4024g917fg0c1b491967a2": ["<i>Yes. </i>Steal bodies. Tear them. Then Illy puts them back together. Again. And again. ", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "f86cdb12-59c3-2fb0-6af5-a4fac65908e4"], "h14875f6dgc5bcg46d6g88f9gca355cc62b40": ["When he wasn't horny for the book. Urgh. Book this. Book that. He loves the book.", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "392ed69e-b7b4-caf5-82c0-3a6cca81ee58"], "h7e1e97ceg5bb2g458ag940dg37e90b8af3a7": ["Hmm. Some light pillage - perhaps a bit of murder to follow?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "d310a8de-aefb-32a4-024c-644fa6005ab2"], "ha240055fgd81dg451dg9c90g2bce89af509f": ["Yes! Master is fun! More fun than Illy.", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "49935997-50ad-8d25-99d3-ad6af59f35c8"], "ha2b1eaeag946ag4498g9c4bgb716974f904b": ["How about another utensil? Fork. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "321977aa-29ca-590a-b816-a7ffb5e1b9be"], "h23eab8ccg69f5g4dcfga481gb2b896e7153c": ["Urgh. <i>Forks. </i>Make the feast slow. Less tearing. Less blood. But fine. I am Fork. ", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "081f8e49-dce5-b7f2-be83-ea4a5327e440"], "h72f2df71g4f66g4b99g885egdcfdae619d88": ["Does Basket sound good to you? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "e37b0707-c5eb-c21a-c7cd-d5c2939fbefe"], "h354c2d67g65bbg4892g800ag673fb242e529": ["Basket. I like. Baskets hold babies. My favourite.", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "5bf7cc58-7e4e-9ac3-70af-7aaf5d5aa96d"], "h9e006284g83acg4a8cg84eag941b17a941b9": ["Yeah. Illy named me. Your friend, the arse wipe, said it was fine. ", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "7018f150-0ff8-f2db-c302-3bdccfefaa28"], "hd5a6449fg192dg41aega5c2g14e2ddc2fe4b": ["Ugh. What chewed you up and spat you out?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "86fced90-b7af-da8f-9234-197dc15d6ba2"], "h937fb366gd651g43c3gb23eg58c05e3ece04": ["Your daddy.", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "47edb98a-e35e-a24d-d73e-fb8010387a5e"], "hcbc8ad20gf4e3g4418gaf2bge76bdfb4cf45": ["Your scroll was in an undead's casket. Who were they?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "aefa0155-79ff-194b-b1c0-f6a12e620f6d"], "h46e59273g667bg44a7ga27fg6e352c9d8c82": ["The blacksmith. The teacher. The grocer. The baker. Little piggies to the butcher.", "81161d0d-06b4-4cfa-db65-95f8a34c31fd", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "de1998f3-5105-2d65-bae7-08adb0c27756"], "h28587fc0g502dg4cb3gbb38g290d1a7f73a5": ["<i>Leave. </i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "2bdb86db-76d8-82d3-f8f9-226113d1efbd"], "hc6d8336fgf141g4429g8c8dg916c4080617e": ["*The stench of sulfur fills your nose.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_ThayanCellar_QuasitSummon.html", "118ec9e8-fd5d-8a62-1f00-885e466b380b"]}